<div id="determine-the-model-accuracy-and-the-cut-off-value" class="section level2">
<h2>Determine the model accuracy and the cut off value</h2>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->
<pre class="r"><code>library(ROCR)
Acc_lasso &lt;- predict(lasso_model1, X_train)
Acc_lasso &lt;- prediction(Acc_lasso,y_train)
eval&lt;-performance(Acc_lasso,&quot;acc&quot;)# plotting a graph between aacuracy and prob values
plot(eval)</code></pre>
<!-- rnb-source-end -->
<!-- rnb-plot-begin eyJjb25kaXRpb25zIjpbXSwiaGVpZ2h0Ijo0MzIuNjMyOSwic2l6ZV9iZWhhdmlvciI6MCwid2lkdGgiOjcwMH0= -->
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<!-- rnb-plot-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->
<!-- rnb-text-begin -->
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxubWF4PC13aGljaC5tYXgoc2xvdChldmFsLFwieS52YWx1ZXNcIilbWzFdXSlcbmFjYzwtc2xvdChldmFsLFwieS52YWx1ZXNcIilbWzFdXVttYXhdI2dpdmVzIHRoZSBwb2ludCBvZiBtYXggYWNjdXJhY3kgb24gdGhlIGN1cnZlXG5wcmludChhY2MpXG5gYGAifQ== -->
<pre class="r"><code>max&lt;-which.max(slot(eval,&quot;y.values&quot;)[[1]])
acc&lt;-slot(eval,&quot;y.values&quot;)[[1]][max]#gives the point of max accuracy on the curve
print(acc)</code></pre>
<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<pre><code>[1] 0.84</code></pre>

<script>

// add bootstrap table styles to pandoc tables
function bootstrapStylePandocTables() {
  $('tr.header').parent('thead').parent('table').addClass('table table-condensed');
}
$(document).ready(function () {
  bootstrapStylePandocTables();
});

$(document).ready(function () {
  $('.knitsql-table').addClass('kable-table');
  var container = $('.kable-table');
  container.each(function() {

    // move the caption out of the table
    var table = $(this).children('table');
    var caption = table.children('caption').detach();
    caption.insertBefore($(this)).css('display', 'inherit');
  });
});

</script>
